content: Online Engagement is there a resource here that we can use to filter/Block MAGA bots and disrupters?   I’m specifically looking for Keyword, Hashtags and phrases that can be used for this purpose.

Hello <@392108353997766659> the auto-mod bot blocks messages with specific words, and the moderators here will see an alert when this happens. We can add to the list of word if you are seeing specific words in suspicious posts. You can also call us in to look at individuals posts by either shairng a link to the post here, or posting a message with "@ moderator" (without a space) somewhere near the a message in any channel. We also have "handling trolls" messaging pinned in the main channels. https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1242249109298221069/1281686666599465040
I am looking for them for the use in other Social Media platforms.
Our server-wide bad words list is not that specific. You can ask the folks in https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1250550849998946417  individuals there may have their own lists.
